Preheat oven to 350 degrees F. Combine the butter, 1/4 cup SPLENDA(R) Brown Sugar Blend and flour until a dough forms. Press into a 13X9 baking pan. Bake for 10 minutes. Blend the eggs, remaining 1/4 cup SPLENDA(R) Brown Sugar Blend, vanilla, flour and baking powder. Stir in the coconut and the pecans. Spread the filling onto the par-baked crust. Return to the oven for 20 minutes.